    <briefdescription>
<para><bold> Specialization of the <ref refid="classcntr_1_1distributed__array" kindref="compound">distributed_array</ref> in which data-blocks are associated with the <ref refid="classcntr_1_1herm__matrix__timestep" kindref="compound">herm_matrix_timestep</ref> objects </bold> </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Purpose</title><para></para>
</simplesect>
Specialization of the <ref refid="classcntr_1_1distributed__array" kindref="compound">distributed_array</ref> for the <ref refid="classcntr_1_1herm__matrix__timestep" kindref="compound">herm_matrix_timestep</ref> objects, which is used for problems, where all ranks need to have the full information [for instance spatial] about the system for a given timestep. In practice the time stepping procedure is used and the last timestep needs to be communicated between all MPI processes. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
